- SCSS Modules: `import styles from "./Component.module.scss"` — use `styles.className` (camelCase only, NO hyphens in class names)
- Motion v12: `import { motion, AnimatePresence } from "motion/react"`
- In SCSS files, use relative paths: `@use "../../styles/variables" as *;` and `@use "../../styles/mixins" as *;`
- Use typed imports: `import type { Candidate } from "@rearden/types"`
- Write ALL files completely — every tsx and scss file mentioned above
